âœ… Secures all URLs
âœ… Provides a default login page
âœ… Requires authentication for everything

ğŸ”¹ Without login: You get 403 Forbidden error ğŸš«
ğŸ”¹ After login: You can access secured pages âœ…
ğŸ”¹ Final Real-Life Example

    Without Security: Anyone can enter your house ğŸ 
    With Security: You need a key (login) to enter ğŸ”‘
    With Authorization: Some rooms are only for admins ğŸšª

