âœ… No SQL! JPA converts this into a database query automatically.
ğŸ”¹ What is Spring Data JPA?

ğŸ‘‰ Spring Data JPA makes JPA even easier by reducing boilerplate code.

ğŸ”¹ Instead of writing queries manually, we just call simple methods, and Spring Data JPA handles everything.
Example: Fetch User by ID

Without Spring Data JPA (JPA Only)

