âœ… No need to write queries! Spring Data JPA handles it.
ğŸ”¹ Why Use Spring Data JPA?

âœ… No need to write SQL manually
âœ… Easy to perform CRUD operations
âœ… Supports multiple databases (MySQL, PostgreSQL, etc.)
âœ… Automatically handles database connections
ğŸ”¹ CRUD Operations in Spring Data JPA

