2ï¸âƒ£ A student has one laptop (One-to-One)
3ï¸âƒ£ A student can enroll in multiple courses (Many-to-Many)

Hibernate helps in managing these relationships automatically.

ğŸ”¹ Final Real-Life Example
Without Hibernate (Manual SQL Queries)

âŒ You have to write SQL manually every time.
With Hibernate (Automatic)

âœ… Hibernate converts Java objects into database tables automatically.
